    "description": "<p>H3 Zoom Pte Ltd&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>67 Ayer Rajah Crescent</p>\n<p>Singapore , 139950</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>__________________________________</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Founded in 2018, we specialize in a comprehensive suite of AI-powered solutions, expertly designed for the built environment ecosystem. We focus on end-to-end continuous monitoring to reduce deferred maintenance costs and quality issues.<br>\n<br>\nOur proprietary, sensor-agnostic technology efficiently processes data from a variety of sources, including 360 cameras, drones, and ground robotics. Targeting real estate, smart cities, and facilities management sectors, we aim to digitise condition assessment and prolong the lifespan of buildings, turning complex data into actionable insights for sustainable and efficient building management.</p>\n<p><br></p>",
